ygData.subject: Question about a good place to go

ygData.messageBody:
I am a Level 4 Wood Elf Warrior and was wondeirng where would be a
good place to go hunting that would have a good profit and kills which won't
be too, too challenging. Also, my guild, The Keepers of the Eternal Elves are
going to be holding a tourney later on which I will have more info on at a
later date. But can someone please tell me a good place?



Jarak, Level 4 Wood Elf Warrior
Member of the Keepers of the Eternal Elves
